# 詞：睇怕

1. 佢成日遲到，睇怕係唔想工作啦。 (He is always late; I'm afraid he doesn't want to work.)
2. 呢個遊戲好難，睇怕連我都玩唔到。 (This game is very difficult; I'm afraid even I can't play it.)
3. 佢話今晚唔返屋企，睇怕係同朋友去飲酒。 (He said he wouldn't come home tonight; I'm afraid he's going out drinking with friends.)
4. 天氣咁熱，睇怕會下雷暴。 (The weather is so hot; I'm afraid there will be a thunderstorm.)
5. 佢個成績好差，睇怕會留級。 (His grades are very poor; I'm afraid he will have to repeat the year.)
6. 你唔好咁心急，睇怕會出錯。 (Don't be so impatient; I'm afraid you might make a mistake.)
7. 呢間店好多人，睇怕要排好耐先至可以買嘢。 (There are so many people in this shop; I'm afraid we'll have to wait a long time before we can buy something.)
8. 佢話會來參加派對，但睇怕係講笑。 (He said he would come to the party, but I'm afraid he's just joking.)
9. 個車好舊，睇怕隨時會壞。 (The car is very old; I'm afraid it might break down anytime.)
10. 你唔好諗住可以偷懶，睇怕老闆會發現。 (Don't think you can slack off; I'm afraid the boss will find out.) [end of text]


